<body>
<bookmark id="bm_id491778684551203" branch="hid/.uno:DraftView" localize="false"/>
<bookmark branch="index" id="bm_id311778717437560">
    <bookmark_value>view;draft view</bookmark_value>
    <bookmark_value>draft view;view</bookmark_value>
</bookmark>
<section id="draftview">
    <h1 id="hd_id951778684551203"><variable id="h1"><link href="text/swriter/01/draft_layout.xhp">Draft View</link></variable></h1>
    <description id="par_id231778684551203">View for distraction-free writing, flattening multi-column sections and disabling whitespace, including left page margin.</description>
</section>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id261778684852813">The Draft View maintains a fixed line width to avoid the overly long text lines caused by window resizing in Web View.</paragraph>
<section id="howtoget">
    <embed href="text/shared/00/00000004.xhp#from_menu_bar"/>
    <paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id831778684833811">Choose <menuitem>View - Draft</menuitem>.</paragraph>
</section>

<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id271778685010956">To focus on distraction-free writing, Draft View supports the followings:</paragraph>
<list type="unordered">
    <listitem>
        <paragraph id="par_id811778684917711"  role="listitem">Hide header and footer;</paragraph>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
        <paragraph id="par_id711778684932850"  role="listitem">Disable <menuitem>View > Whitespace</menuitem> to remove top and bottom page margins and space between pages;</paragraph>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
        <paragraph id="par_id491778684951116"  role="listitem">Hide the left page margin when <menuitem>View > Whitespace</menuitem> is disabled, so that all body text (e.g., in mirrored page layouts with different left margins) starts at the same distance from the left page border.</paragraph>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
        <paragraph id="par_id161778684959608"  role="listitem">Show multi-column sections as single-column sections. It keeps the original column width, if it is possible, that is, when all the columns have the same width.</paragraph>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
        <paragraph id="par_id571778684966378"  role="listitem">Changing to Normal View from Draft View, restore the setting of <menuitem>View > Whitespace</menuitem>.</paragraph>
    </listitem>
</list>
<note id="par_id611778684981222">Similar to the Hidden whitespace mode, the Draft View setting is not saved yet.</note>
</body>
